---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for AIatolah — Information on cookies, data collection, and Google AdSense compliance."
>
  <main class="privacy-container">

    <section class="privacy-hero">
      <h1>Privacy <span class="ai-highlight">Policy</span></h1>
      <p class="tagline">Compliance, cookies, and data transparency.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="privacy-body glass-panel">

      <div class="privacy-block">
        <h2>1. Overview</h2>
        <p>
          At AIatolah, accessible from aiatolah.com, the privacy of our visitors is of extreme importance to us. 
          This Privacy Policy document outlines the types of personal information received and collected by AIatolah 
          and how it is used.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-block">
        <h2>2. Log Files</h2>
        <p>
          Like many other websites, AIatolah makes use of log files. The information inside the log files includes 
          internet protocol (IP) addresses, browser type, Internet Service Provider (ISP), date/time stamp, referring/exit pages, 
          and number of clicks to analyze trends, administer the site, track user's movement around the site, and gather demographic information. 
          IP addresses and other such information are not linked to any information that is personally identifiable.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-block">
        <h2>3. Cookies and Web Beacons</h2>
        <p>
          AIatolah uses cookies to store information about visitors' preferences, to record user-specific information on which pages the user accesses or visits, 
          and to customize web page content based on visitors' browser type or other information that the visitor sends via their browser.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-block">
        <h2>4. Google AdSense & DART Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Google, as a third-party vendor, uses cookies to serve ads on AIatolah.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Google's use of the DART cookie enables it to serve ads to users based on their visit to AIatolah and other sites on the Internet.</li>
          <li>Users may opt out of the use of the DART cookie by visiting the Google Ad and Content Network Privacy Policy at the following URL: <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: #00d4ff;">https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads</a>.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Our third-party ad servers or ad networks use technology to serve the advertisements and links that appear on AIatolah directly to your browsers. 
          They automatically receive your IP address when this occurs. Other technologies (such as cookies, JavaScript, or Web Beacons) may also be used by 
          the third-party ad networks to measure the effectiveness of their advertisements and/or to personalize the advertising content that you see.
        </p>
        <p>
          AIatolah has no access to or control over these cookies that are used by third-party advertisers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-block">
        <h2>5. Third-Party Privacy Policies</h2>
        <p>
          You should consult the respective privacy policies of these third-party ad servers for more detailed information on their practices as well as for instructions 
          about how to opt-out of certain practices. AIatolah's privacy policy does not apply to, and we cannot control the activities of, such other advertisers or web sites.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you wish to disable cookies, you may do so through your individual browser options. More detailed information about cookie management with specific web browsers 
          can be found at the browsers' respective websites.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-block">
        <h2>6. Consent</h2>
        <p>
          By using our website, you hereby consent to our privacy policy and agree to its terms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-block">
        <h2>7. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you require any more information or have any questions about our privacy policy, please feel free to contact us by email at <a href="mailto:migueldorosario@gmail.com" style="color: #00d4ff; text-decoration: none;">migueldorosario@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .privacy-container {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .privacy-hero {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .privacy-hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }

  .ai-highlight {
    color: #00d4ff;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .privacy-body {
    padding: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .privacy-block h2 {
    font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #00d4ff;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .privacy-block p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .privacy-block ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .privacy-block ul li {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .privacy-block ul li::before {
    content: '▸';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #00d4ff;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .privacy-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
    .privacy-body { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
